    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The metro is no longer a place of transit. It's a <strong>tomb</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In <i>Hunted Within the Metro</i></strong>, you break free from underground imprisonment only to discover that escape is far more complicated than survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315920/extras/945c3e9dc831103c789e8ffe5b76f8a0.poster.avif?t=1772093062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315920/extras/945c3e9dc831103c789e8ffe5b76f8a0.webm?t=1772093062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pilot your own survival train</strong> through an abandoned metro system ,it's your mobile base, your refuge, and your key to reaching new areas, From <strong>Dark Tunnels, and Underworld Caverns ,to Frozen Surface.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315920/extras/0f3523b3b57fcd16920ff03b6929764f.poster.avif?t=1772093062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315920/extras/0f3523b3b57fcd16920ff03b6929764f.webm?t=1772093062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315920/extras/0f3523b3b57fcd16920ff03b6929764f.mp4?t=1772093062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight Diverse Threats:</strong> <strong>Giant scorpions</strong>, burrowing <strong>mutant worms</strong>, and other <strong>monsters</strong> and <strong>abominations</strong> using an arsenal of <strong>weapons</strong> <strong>melee</strong> <strong>,pistol, shotgun, and SMG</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beware:</strong> <strong>twisted traps</strong> are sometimes deadlier than beasts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scavenge supplies, gather resources ,craft weapons</strong>, complete missions, and gradually uncover the conspiracy that put you in chains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Every tunnel leads somewhere. Every choice brings you closer to escape ,or deeper into the nightmare.</i></p>",
